  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Temporal Critical Flows — Overview",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 11,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "\n**Critical-path monitoring — works on Temporal Cloud AND self-hosted OSS, same panels.**\nA compact view of the operations that most directly affect application health.\n\nThis stack watches three critical flows:\n\n1. **Starting / Signaling** — `StartWorkflowExecution`, `SignalWorkflowExecution` (client API creating/modifying workflow state). Target a tight latency budget here.\n2. **Workflow Progress** — workers polling (`PollWorkflowTaskQueue`, `PollActivityTaskQueue`) and completing work (`Respond*`).\n\nUse the **Critical Flows** dropdown (top-left) to drill into each flow + Worker Tuning.\n\n> **How the backend-agnostic panels work:** each RPS/error/latency panel below carries two query\n> targets — one against the OSS metric (raw counter, `rate()`'d) and one against the Cloud\n> `temporal_cloud_v1_*` equivalent (already a precomputed rate, never `rate()`'d). Whichever\n> backend you're actually running populates the panel; the other target just returns no data.\n> No manual datasource switching needed — both metric families land in the same `prometheus-kind`\n> store already (in-cluster Prometheus scrapes SDK pods + the Temporal Cloud OpenMetrics endpoint\n> and remote_writes both here).\n>\n> **What can't be unified:** persistence, internal task processing, shard, and process-level\n> metrics are below the customer-facing API boundary — Temporal Cloud is a managed control plane\n> and never exposes them, on any topology. Those live in the **Temporal Self-Hosted Internals**\n> folder instead of pretending they'd populate here.\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Frontend — Critical Operations",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 11
      },
      "id": 2,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Critical Frontend RPS by Operation",
      "description": "OSS: service_requests (rate). Cloud: temporal_cloud_v1_service_request_count (precomputed rate, no rate()).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-kind"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 12
      },
      "id": 3,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-kind"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (operation) (rate(service_requests{operation=~\"StartWorkflowExecution|SignalWorkflowExecution|SignalWithStartWorkflowExecution|RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted|RespondActivityTaskCompleted|PollWorkflowTaskQueue|PollActivityTaskQueue\"}[$rate]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{operation}}"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-kind"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (operation) (temporal_cloud_v1_service_request_count{operation=~\"StartWorkflowExecution|SignalWorkflowExecution|SignalWithStartWorkflowExecution|RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted|RespondActivityTaskCompleted|PollWorkflowTaskQueue|PollActivityTaskQueue\"})",
          "legendFormat": "{{operation}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Critical Frontend Errors by Operation",
      "description": "OSS: service_errors (rate). Cloud: temporal_cloud_v1_service_error_count (precomputed rate, no rate()).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-kind"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 12
      },
      "id": 4,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-kind"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (operation) (rate(service_errors{operation=~\"StartWorkflowExecution|SignalWorkflowExecution|SignalWithStartWorkflowExecution|RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted|RespondActivityTaskCompleted|PollWorkflowTaskQueue|PollActivityTaskQueue\"}[$rate]) OR on() vector(0))",
          "legendFormat": "{{operation}}"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-kind"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (operation) (temporal_cloud_v1_service_error_count{operation=~\"StartWorkflowExecution|SignalWorkflowExecution|SignalWithStartWorkflowExecution|RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted|RespondActivityTaskCompleted|PollWorkflowTaskQueue|PollActivityTaskQueue\"})",
          "legendFormat": "{{operation}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Critical Frontend Latency p99 by Operation",
      "description": "Latency thresholds: yellow 200ms, red 1s. OSS: histogram_quantile over service_latency_bucket. Cloud: temporal_cloud_v1_service_latency_p99 (already a percentile — combined across any extra dimensions with max, not sum).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-kind"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 20
      },
      "id": 5,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "thresholdsStyle": {
              "mode": "line"
            }
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 0.2
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-kind"
          },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (operation, le) (rate(service_latency_bucket{operation=~\"StartWorkflowExecution|SignalWorkflowExecution|SignalWithStartWorkflowExecution|RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted|RespondActivityTaskCompleted|PollWorkflowTaskQueue|PollActivityTaskQueue\"}[$rate])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{operation}}"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-kind"
          },
          "expr": "max by (operation) (temporal_cloud_v1_service_latency_p99{operation=~\"StartWorkflowExecution|SignalWorkflowExecution|SignalWithStartWorkflowExecution|RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted|RespondActivityTaskCompleted|PollWorkflowTaskQueue|PollActivityTaskQueue\"})",
          "legendFormat": "{{operation}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
